						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: <hi rend="italic">Vishu, Mārgaḻi</hi> 13.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is in characters of the 17th century A.D. It is damaged in the middle. It records a gift of garden to the temple of Koḻundīśvarasvāmin for the merit of the Mahārāja-saheb, probably the Mahrāṭha ruler of Tanjore.</p>						

